							<span class="text-gray-600 text-sm">September 2023 - Present</span>
						</div>
						<p class="text-gray-600">Rutgers University, New Jersey</p>
						<p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Specialization: Motor Control and Human Movement</p>
