							<span class="text-gray-600 text-sm">September 2023 - May 2025</span>
						</div>
						<p class="text-gray-600">Rutgers University, New Jersey</p>
						<p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Thesis: Interpretable biomarkers for cognitive load utilizing drawing data from consumer-grade tablets</p>
					</div>

					<div>
						<div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-1">
							<h3 class="font-bold text-lg">Bachelor's Degree</h3>
