					</div>
					
					<div class="text-gray-700">
						<p>Torres, E. B., <strong>Vero, J.</strong>, Drain, N., Rai, R., & Bermperidis, T. (2025). Hidden social and emotional competencies in autism spectrum disorders captured through the digital lens. <em>Frontiers in Psychiatry, 16</em>, 1559202.</p>
					</div>
					
