						<p>Torres, E. B., Bermperidis, T., Varkey, H., <strong>Vero, J.</strong>, London, E., Phan, H., Kittler, P., ... (2022). Sensing Echoes: Temporal misalignment as the Earliest Marker of Neurodevelopmental Derail. <em>SSRN</em> 4049202.</p>
					</div>
					
