					<li>Planning-execution loop in motor behavior</li>
					<li>Typical and atypical movement patterns</li>
					<li>Environmental influences on motor control</li>
					<li>Human-computer interaction in motor assessment</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<!-- Additional Information -->
			<section>
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-gray-200">Additional Information</h2>
